---
import { COMPANY_CONTENT } from "@/content";
import AltLayout from "@/layouts/AltLayout.astro";
---

<AltLayout title="Terms of Use">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Terms of Use</h1>

    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Overview</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Welcome to my sample pack and VST plugin site. By downloading or using
        the content from this site, you're agreeing to these simple terms. These
        samples and plugins are created to help musicians make awesome music.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Using My Samples & Plugins</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
        <li>
          Feel free to use all samples and VST plugins in your music, both
          personal and commercial projects.
        </li>
        <li>
          You can't resell these samples or plugins as your own products or
          include them in your own sample packs for distribution.
        </li>
        <li>Credit is appreciated but not required.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Account Stuff</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        If you create an account, keep your password safe and don't share it.
        You're responsible for anything that happens under your account.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Content Quality</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        I work hard to create high-quality samples and plugins, but everything
        is provided "as is" without any warranties. If something isn't working,
        let me know and I'll try to fix it.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about these terms? Contact me at {COMPANY_CONTENT.email}.</p>
    </section>
  </main>
</AltLayout>
